from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
In [ ]:
for n in range(1, 15):
    algorithm = KMeans(n_clusters=n, init='k-means++', n_init=10, max_iter=300, tol=0.0001, random_state=32)
    algorithm.fit(x1)
    inertia.append(algorithm.inertia_)
